339
00:12:23,058 --> 00:12:24,842
okay, if you've gone
over every case file,

340
00:12:24,893 --> 00:12:26,560
then you know
that the reason nobody wins

341
00:12:26,645 --> 00:12:28,545
is because there is no chink
in the armor.

