348
00:12:46,698 --> 00:12:47,915
It's our story
versus theirs.

349
00:12:47,999 --> 00:12:50,000
It's a shady deal
and a case full of cash.

350
00:12:50,068 --> 00:12:51,418
Their story is going
to be more compelling.

351
00:12:51,503 --> 00:12:54,254
