389
00:14:13,168 --> 00:14:16,319
He always takes my calls.

390
00:14:16,371 --> 00:14:18,172
Hi, it's Nick.
Leave a message.

391
00:14:18,256 --> 00:14:21,208
Let me tell you
what that message really said.

392
00:14:21,292 --> 00:14:22,843
"Hi, Ava.
It's Nick.

393
00:14:22,927 --> 00:14:24,887
